LEE
v.
FREEMAN 190P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2017 Brandon Lee, for Lee, Brandon Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Freeman, James.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th of June 2017 by Plaintiff for Appeal of Decision of the North Carolina State Bar:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of August 2017."
